mixin specialThanksSection()
  style.
    .content {
      padding: 50px;
      margin: 0;
      color: white;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 4em;
      color: white;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.5em;
      color: white;
      margin: 10px 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .thanks-list {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      text-align: left;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .thanks-list li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

  .content
    h1 Special Thanks

    p At The Cartel Marketplace, we would like to extend our heartfelt gratitude to everyone who has contributed to our journey.

    h2 Our Partners
    p Thank you to our amazing partners and sellers for trusting us to showcase their products. Your dedication and quality offerings make our marketplace vibrant and diverse.

    h2 Our Team
    p A special shoutout to our incredible team whose hard work and passion drive The Cartel forward every day. Your commitment to excellence is the backbone of our success.

    h2 Our Customers
    p To our valued customers, thank you for choosing The Cartel as your shopping destination. Your support and feedback inspire us to continuously improve and innovate.

    h2 Community Support
    p We also want to acknowledge the communities that support us. Your engagement and enthusiasm fuel our mission to create a better shopping experience for everyone.

    p Together, we are building a marketplace that values quality, trust, and connection. Thank you for being part of The Cartel family!
